.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, daisy, dahlia, zinnia, iris
5 different games are played: bridge, canasta, domino, whist, poker
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: salsa, folk, techno, d&b, indie
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: balloon-flowermaster, december, november, may, march
The people have 5 different jobs:  piloterman, writer, photographer, pilot, freelancer
1. the person playing bridge is the person who growsdahlia
2. the person playing swedish is the photographer
3. the person playing canasta is the fan of d&b
4. the person who growsdaisy is on the left of the person who growszinnia
5. the person who growsdaisy is the fan of folk
6. the person who's birthday is in november is the writer
7. the person who growsiris is the person who's birthday is in december
8. the fan of techno is in the middle
9. the person playing whist is on the far left
10. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left or right of the piloterman
11. the freelancers is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in december
12. the person who's birthday is in balloon-flowermaster is the fan of salsa
13. the person playing domino is the person who's birthday is in may
14. the person playing whist is on the left or right of the person who growsballoon-flower
15. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left or right of the fan of indie

.:: Answer ::.
